OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FFormer soldier Daniel Khalife has
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty partway through his
OL,8,Ftrial to escaping from prison under a
OL,9,Ffood truck.
OL,11,FKhalife, 23, changed his plea to a
OL,12,Fcharge of escaping from lawful custody
OL,13,Fhalfway through his trial at Woolwich
OL,14,FCrown Court.
OL,16,FHe continues to deny the spying and
OL,17,Fterrorism charges against him. The ex-
OL,18,Fsoldier is accused of gathering
OL,19,Finformation for Iran.
