OL,3,CFormer soldier Daniel Khalife pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to prison escape
OL,6,FKhalife escaped from HMP Wandsworth in
OL,7,Fsouth-west London in September 2023 by
OL,8,Fclinging to the underside of a food
OL,9,Fdelivery truck using a sling made from
OL,10,Fkitchen trousers.
OL,12,FHe escaped in the hope he would be
OL,13,Fkept in a high-security unit (HSU) at
OL,14,Fa different prison, away from "sex
OL,15,Foffenders" and "terrorists" after his
OL,16,Frecapture, he previously told his
OL,17,Ftrial at Woolwich Crown Court.
