OL,6,FMrs Justice Bobbie Cheema-Grubb told
OL,7,Fjurors she had asked Khalife if he
OL,8,Fwanted the prison escape charge to be
OL,9,Fput to him again.
OL,11,FWhen the charge was put to the former
OL,12,Fsoldier, he replied: "I'm guilty."
OL,14,FThe court heard he planned a fake
OL,15,Fescape attempt for August 21 in the
OL,16,Fhope he would be moved to the HSU, but
OL,17,Fdecided that a genuine escape was his
OL,18,Fonly option after the incident was not
OL,19,Freported to senior prison staff.
