OL,6,FKhalife wanted to be kept in the HSU
OL,7,Fat HMP Belmarsh ` a prison within a
OL,8,Fprison holding some of the country's
OL,9,Fmost dangerous criminals ` because he
OL,10,Fbelieved he would be safer there, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard.
OL,13,FFive days before his successful
OL,14,Fescape, he attached a sling to the
OL,15,Funderside of the lorry made from
OL,16,Fkitchen trousers and carabiners.
OL,18,FThe sling "wasn't spotted at
OL,19,FWandsworth gate or any other prison",
OL,20,FKhalife said.
