OL,6,F"When the tail lift raised it covered
OL,7,Fme entirely," he continued.
OL,9,F"If the makeshift sling wasn't
OL,10,Fnoticed, they're hardly going to
OL,11,Fnotice me."
OL,13,FWhile on the run, Khalife bought
OL,14,Fclothes from Marks & Spencer and a
OL,15,Fcoffee from McDonald's, and walked
OL,16,Fbeside the River Thames before being
OL,17,Fcaught by police three days later.
OL,19,F"I accept that I left the prison and I
OL,20,Fdidn't have any permission," he told
OL,21,Fjurors.
